Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:93339,97010}{\i1}Nozomi was attacked by yakuza\Nand had her guitar broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:41.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:97010,101097}{\i1}That event opened her eyes to what\None can expect in the adult world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:48.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:102140,108896}{\i1}It was the same yakuza that calmed her down\Nand gave her the motivation to continue working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:02:00.90,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:113401,120908}{\fad(1000,1000)}— Episode 06 —\NA Golden Opportunity{NOTE:第6話\\N訪れたチャンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:123661,125663}Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.24,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:125663,127248}Hey! Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:09.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:127248,129959}Nozomi-chan!\NHey, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:129959,132211}What's going on?\NWhy are you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:15.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:132211,135882}How could I not be?\NI'll explain everything in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.38,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:137342,140386}Anyway, just stay calm.\NI have to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:22.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:140386,142096}Stay calm?\NTake your own advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.89,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:142096,144891}No. Yes. Maybe. Anyway!\NJust wait till you hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.64,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:144891,148644}You remember that Tatsu guy\Nfrom the Kashima Group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:34.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:148644,154108}Tatsu-san? You mean the boss of the yakuza\Nthat bullied me, who you later talked to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.15,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:154108,155151}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:40.15,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:155151,160156}That Tatsu fella took the trouble to provide me\Nwith an information that could be very useful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:160156,163493}You know a bar called Mimi\Ndown the street, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:163493,166204}Yes. Their barmaid is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.66,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:166204,170666}Well, a famous composer has recently started\Nto come there. Egawa, Uegawa or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:54.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:170666,174128}By Egawa, you mean Egawa Isao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:174128,176172}Oh? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:176172,178007}How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:03.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:178007,183721}He's one of the most famous composers of our\Ntime and wrote a lot of very well known songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.68,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:183721,186682}I didn't know he was so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:11.56,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:186682,191562}Nozomi-chan, opportunity like this\Ndoesn't knock twice. You have to seize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:191562,193314}Seize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:18.23,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:193314,198236}We're gonna have that big shot\Ncomposer fella hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.94,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:198236,201948}Once he does, he'll help you\Nget into the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:25.45,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:201948,205451}I'm sure he'll see\Nthe talent in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:205451,206494}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:206494,209580}That would be terrific\Nif it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:218089,220299}I feel so comfortable\Nwhen I come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:220299,223261}This bar perfectly reflects\Nyour personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:48.85,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:223261,228850}Oh, no, please don't flatter me.\NDo you want to embarrass me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:58.31,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:233646,238317}People like me are surrounded\Nby music all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:04.40,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:238317,244407}{\fscx95}I can't tell how relaxing it is for me to be able to take\Nrefuge in a place as calm and peaceful as your bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:246367,248744}{\i1}Uncle was right, he really is\Nthe real Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:248744,252123}{\i1}If I let slip this opportunity,\NI could never meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:12.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:252123,252999}{\i1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:252999,256461}{\i1}Enough thinking, time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:256461,259547}Good evening, gentlemen.\NHow about a little song?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:262758,264343}Good evening, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.97,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:264343,266971}I'm sorry, but let's do it\Nsome other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:31.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:266971,271476}You've always been so good to me.\NI'll sing for free tonight to show my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:41.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:274020,281736}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The bride on the night train  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:花嫁は 夜汽車にのって }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:281736,285156}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  She's getting married—  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:とついでゆくの あの人の }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.07,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:285156,286073}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.08,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:294832,297084}I'm… sorry I snapped at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:03.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:300296,303049}I don't want to listen\Nto any songs tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:06.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:303049,306886}I just want to sit quietly\Nand enjoy my drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:306886,309138}The bartender was so kind that\Nshe listened to my selfish request,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.60,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:309138,312600}and turned down other\Nstreet musicians before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:312600,315645}I didn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:315645,317146}I'm sorry, Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:317146,318439}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.56,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:318439,319565}Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:319565,320316}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.07,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:320316,324070}Then let me tell you\Na word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.07,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:324070,326072}Please listen to me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.24,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:326072,329242}Music is to calm people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:329242,333162}If you really like music,\Ndo not annoy people with your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:333162,335331}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:335331,337542}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.87,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:337542,338876}See you soon, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:338876,340211}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:346801,349845}Egawa-sensei is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:54.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:349845,354684}I hadn't ever thought about the mood of my\Naudience. I just wanted to get his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:59.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:354684,359230}This is not how a real singer behaves.\NIt just means that I'm not qualified as a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.27,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:359230,361274}No. You have that wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:06.36,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:361274,366362}Alcohol and music are supposed\Nto go together since forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:14.32,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:366362,374328}You can't give up just because some douchebag\Nsent you off. I won't forgive him for this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.08,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:374328,377081}You always intercede\Nfor Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.79,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:377081,378791}Well, duh, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:378791,381043}I may not look like it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:27.00,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:381043,387008}I'm Nozomi-chan's\Nnumber one supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:387008,390344}Uh… What on earth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:390344,393097}What is this, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.93,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:393097,395933}Huh? Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.26,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:395933,398269}Don't you "oh, you're right" me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.39,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:398269,402398}You oughta be more careful,\Nor you'll run into trouble with the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.73,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:402398,404734}Here, let's have a little inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.86,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:404734,405860}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.32,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:405860,408321}What is this? This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:409822,411449}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.40,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:411449,413409}I'm not very good at it,\Njust like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:07:00.45,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:415161,420458}I had to take over the business in such a haste.\NLet's hope Dad gets better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:420458,421834}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:433471,435931}How are your eyes, Mom?\NDon't tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:23.52,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:438184,443522}No, it's okay. Yesterday I had to stay up very late,\Nso my eyes are a little tired. But it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:443522,445608}I see. That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.19,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:445608,447193}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:459997,461957}The home of the biggest stars,\Nthe Orion Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:461957,465336}I hope you have everything arranged for me.\NI do not want to sound ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.46,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:465336,466462}It'll be fine, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:52.05,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:466462,472051}Sakagami-san, the production manager, is a cousin\Nof your father's company executive director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.97,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:472051,474970}I have already talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.26,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:474970,476263}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.97,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:479100,480976}What do you think?\NNice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.98,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:484772,487983}Here is one of the singers\Nthat we intend to launch soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:487983,488984}Orion Records\N"A Rising Star"\NKishimoto Haru{NOTE:オリオンレコードのほに放つ\\N"大型新人"\\N岸本はる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:10.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:489985,490986}Queen of the 20th century{NOTE:20世紀の女王}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:492154,494156}A rising star\Nof the new 70's era{NOTE:７０年時代に送る 大型 新人歌手}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.16,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:494156,498160}A rising star{NOTE:新人歌手}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:23.16,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:498160,503165}A rising star{NOTE:新人歌手}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.66,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:502081,505668}Frankly, her voice is barely better\Nthan that of an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:29.79,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:505668,509797}When it comes to singers' redeeming features,\Nthe standards have degraded over time a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.75,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:509797,512758}Can someone with so little talent\Nreally become a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.88,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:512758,514885}More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.88,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:514885,518889}Excellent recording technology\Nand large-scale advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.76,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:518889,522768}Finally, a good teacher\Nto raise the newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.56,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:522768,526564}So do you already know who\Nis going to teach my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:52.36,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:526564,532361}I was thinking about the best-selling composer\Nof the modern era, Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.53,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:532361,535531}But he's known for accepting\Nvery few students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:59.45,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:535531,539452}It won't be easy to convince him\Nto give lessons to someone he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.95,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:542246,544957}I believe you can make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.79,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:544957,546792}I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.79,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:546792,548794}Reception room\NDo not disturb
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.58,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:549628,551589}That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.17,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:551589,554175}I'd be really happy if you accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.09,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:554175,557094}I'd like some time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:21.22,Default,Sakagami,0,0,0,,{TIME:557094,561223}You'll be well paid.\NI'm leaving her in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:561223,563225}Ah, Sakagami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:564185,566103}What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:566103,568397}Let me hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:568397,569148}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.60,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:569148,570608}Do your best, Miki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.69,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:572777,575696}I leave the song up to you.\NIt can be your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:575696,578532}I'll sing "The harmony of love", then.{NOTE:愛に生き 平和に生きる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:45.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:579909,585331}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When you choose the way of love  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:人は愛に生き}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:50.37,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:585331,590377}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  everything becomes right.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:平和に生きる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:55.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:590377,595633}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  What was your happiness  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:一人の幸せは}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:56.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:595633,596509}Alright, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.34,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:596509,597343}Oh, so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.01,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:597343,599011}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:599011,603057}Aside from the matter of your voice,\Nwhat you did here was a mere imitation at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:603057,605935}But I didn't try to imitate anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.93,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:605935,608938}You have to sing\Nfrom the bottom of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.81,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:608938,610815}This means… I've failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.94,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:610815,613943}Please, Maestro, maybe there's\Nsomething we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.52,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:613943,616529}Give my daughter\Nat least a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:616529,618531}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:24.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:620825,624119}You see, I believe Sakagami-san can,\Nto a certain degree, recognize talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:625204,628123}That's why I agreed\Nto listen to your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:34.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:628123,634421}But let me make this clear: in this business,\Ntalent is the greatest weapon you can have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:634421,638801}Therefore, when I realized that your daughter\Ndoesn't possess the makings of a good singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:638801,642888}I've decided she's not worth\Nmy time, to put it bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.68,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:642888,645683}So my official answer is that\NI won't be teaching your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:650396,652857}You really auditioned, Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:652857,656235}If you don't believe, call Orion Records\Nand find out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:656235,658863}I'm going to tell you\Nwhat you're going to hear:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:03.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:658863,663033}that Kōda Miki was entrusted\Nto the famous Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.86,Default,Kōda Miki's follower,0,0,0,,{TIME:663033,664869}That's a magnificent news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.99,Default,Kōda Miki's follower,0,0,0,,{TIME:664869,666996}You're so good at everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:666996,668497}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:14.16,Default,Kōda Miki's follower,0,0,0,,{TIME:668497,674169}Egawa-sensei must've been speechless\Nwhen he heard you sing, Kōda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.54,Default,Kōda Miki's follower,0,0,0,,{TIME:674169,677548}He said he was certain\Nshe'd make an outstanding career.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:677548,680217}I see. I'm happy for you, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:680217,681468}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:25.30,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:681468,685306}I'd like to thank you,\Nbut actually it's not that big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:686307,687725}At least, to me it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:28.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:687725,688559}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:688559,691061}If I wasn't born into a Kōda family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:35.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:691061,695482}and was some nameless, poor girl, I don't think\Na chance like that would come my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:38.15,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:695482,698152}The director of the\Nrecord company and Egawa Isao
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.78,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:698152,701780}only ended up lowering their heads\Nin front of my dad's money and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:701780,705367}No. Egawa-sensei is not a person\Nyou can buy with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:705367,707828}Oh? How would you know,\Ndo you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:707828,711373}I ran into him once in a bar\Nwhere I sometimes sing at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:56.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:711373,716420}I had the opportunity to talk to him\Nand he taught me what true music is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:716420,718547}He made me understand\Nthat it's about the love for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:718547,721258}If he was the type that bows\Nto money and power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:06.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:721258,726639}I don't think he'd be able to create\Nsuch deep and moving pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:726639,727723}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:727723,731894}But he didn't bat an eye when he was\Ntaking money my mother gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:731894,734104}I don't care about your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.81,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:734104,736815}I saw with my own eyes\Nwhat kind of man he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:736815,738817}It's not true.\NIt's a bunch of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:738817,740819}Who do you expect\Nto believe this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:744365,745658}{\i1}Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.49,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:745658,748494}{\i1}What kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:33.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:748494,753332}{\i1}Nozomi came to think that Egawa Isao\Nbelonged to a world out of her reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.21,Default,Trainee,0,0,0,,{TIME:763384,764218}Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:44.84,Default,Trainee,0,0,0,,{TIME:764218,764843}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:764843,765636}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:768555,770140}It's Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:53.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:771183,773143}Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:774061,776146}Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:777189,778899}Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:778899,779817}Funny!
Comment: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:02.48,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:782486,782486}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.28,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:787157,789284}So you're afraid your mother\Nis losing her sight…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.91,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:789284,790911}Is that what's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:790911,791996}That too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:16.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:791996,796000}But I'd like to ask you about\NEgawa Isao, Miki-san's new teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:804717,807511}It's not true.\NI'm sure she lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:807511,808804}But what if…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:35.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:810931,815019}What if Egawa-sensei really is\Nthe kind of person Miki-san claims he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:43.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:816186,823527}When I think he really is like that, I feel very\Ndisappointed and lose my motivation to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:51.57,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:823527,831577}So you now want me to judge who is telling\Nthe truth, you or Miki-san. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:831577,833120}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.62,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:833120,834621}There's only one valid answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.24,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:834621,836248}I believe in you.\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:836248,838167}You believe in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:02.12,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:838167,842129}You're hoping that your role model,\Nthat Egawa guy, is in fact worth of your respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.84,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:842129,845841}Meanwhile, that rich kid Kōda\Nsays he's easily bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.71,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:845841,848719}You forget that I've never met\Nthe man to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:13.14,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:848719,853140}If you're asking me who I'm going to back,\Nthe answer is kind of obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.14,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:853140,854141}Trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.89,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:859855,861899}Don't let it mess\Nwith your head too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.23,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:861899,864234}I have boxing.\NYou have music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:864234,865527}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.65,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:865527,868655}Ultimately, what matters to us\Nare the skills and the effort we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.78,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:868655,870783}Money or social status\Nhave nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.82,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:870783,871825}Alright, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:873327,874870}Ah… Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.49,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:876371,877498}Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:878540,881335}Funny! See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:883796,886173}{\i1}It all boils down\Nto skill and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:886173,887341}{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887341,892346}{\i1}I'll do my best and seize\Nthe first opportunity I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:892346,894389}{\i1}Thank you, Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:58.97,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:894389,898977}Egawa Isao{NOTE:江川いさお}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.86,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:905192,906860}Let's end here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:906860,908612}Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:908612,910489}Do you think I'll be ready soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:910489,911365}Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:911365,914284}To record my first disk.\NMy mom is curious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:914284,916328}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.74,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:916328,919748}Tell to your mother:\Nthis is not a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:22.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:919748,922042}In my eyes, for now\Nit's out of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:26.21,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:922042,926213}Even street singers\Nare better than you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:926213,927714}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.43,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:932928,936431}You don't need to be\Nso spiteful towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:936431,938183}Spiteful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:938183,940602}There's a girl named Mine Nozomi\Nin my class who sings in the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:940602,943063}It's her you were\Ntalking about, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:944398,946733}Mine Nozomi?\NNow that you mention it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:946733,948402}Yes, that might've been her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:52.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:948402,952239}If you get be too close to her,\Nyou may risk your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:56.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:952239,956118}She might look sweet and innocent,\Nbut she's a quite the bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:16:01.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:956118,961039}For example, her dad got\Nstabbed in a fight with yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:961039,962124}Kōda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:05.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:962124,965419}I hardly even know this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:965419,968547}But I find it petty on your part to peddle\Nsuch gossip. You should be ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:968547,970883}But sir, I only spoke the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:970883,972134}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.02,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:987065,988025}Oh, it's you, Maestro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.61,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:989401,991612}You're rather early tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:35.74,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:991612,995741}Yes, indeed. You'll have to excuse me, but\Ntonight I just wanted to ask you for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:995741,998827}Do you remember this young singer\Nwho came here the other night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.95,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:998827,1000954}Ah, Nozomi-chan?\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.66,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000954,1005667}If I had known that she was such a decent girl,\NI wouldn't have treated her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005667,1008503}I came to regret it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.71,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008503,1012716}If you want to meet her in person,\Nshe should be… let me think…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.51,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012716,1015510}I think at this time she\Nshould be at the Moon River.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015510,1018680}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:05.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018680,1025520}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:10.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026396,1030651}Thank you and I hope\Nyou liked my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030651,1032402}Should I sing you another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.61,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032402,1034613}Nah, thanks.\NYou can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:18.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034613,1038116}Excuse me, sir, but you\Ndidn't give me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.45,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038116,1041453}What? You want to\Nswindle money out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041453,1043580}No. It's you who asked me\Nto sing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043580,1045832}You have to give me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.50,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045832,1047501}What is wrong with you, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.75,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049294,1052756}Here I am sitting quietly in my corner,\Nthen you come by and ask me if I want a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.55,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052756,1055550}I just replied, okay, do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.38,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055550,1058387}I don't remember agreeing\Nto pay you a single penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.42,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058387,1059429}Now scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061139,1063517}Oh, it's you, Kuma-san.\NHow long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.89,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063517,1065894}I'm your number one supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.85,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065894,1068855}It's my duty to protect you\Nand collect your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1068855,1070857}– Step aside.\N– What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.23,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070857,1072234}Hey there, dandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.23,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072234,1074236}What are you doing?\NWho the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074236,1077489}You don't get to talk.\NI hate stupid rich guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:02.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077489,1082953}You're going to pay what you owe\Nto our Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:05.03,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082953,1085038}I-I can't breathe!\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085038,1086915}Stop it. Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.54,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086915,1089543}It's okay. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.87,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089543,1090877}Alright, time to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:11.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090877,1091670}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095299,1097009}Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097968,1099303}Ah, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100429,1101138}Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101138,1102431}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102431,1104141}You dirty little thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111815,1113692}It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114651,1116111}{\i1}Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:49.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124453,1129833}{\i1}It was a great chance for Nozomi,\Nwho had neither money nor social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129833,1133712}{\i1}But that dream\Nwas torn in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:19:00.71,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1136214,1140719}{\fad(0,1500)}Orion Records\NOfficial Store
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:58.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135130,1138884}{\i1}If you don't believe, call Orion Records\Nand find out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138884,1142429}{\i1}You'll hear that Kōda Miki was\Nentrusted to the famous Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:08.01,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142429,1148018}{\i1}That she's a promising singer\Nwho is soon going to sell out in a big way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154399,1155359}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156193,1157277}{\i1}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157277,1160739}{\i1}You dirty little thief.\NYou dirty little thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169456,1172042}What's your problem,\Nyou part-time gangster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.41,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172042,1174419}Wanna start a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:35.71,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174419,1175712}You bet I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.54,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175712,1177547}She's at a sensitive age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:42.42,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177547,1182427}How are you going to apologize to her mother\Nif something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.63,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182427,1185639}Yeah, and I told you\NI went looking for her right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.22,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185639,1188225}I don't think I've done\Nanything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.97,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188225,1190977}What else did you\Nexpect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.93,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190977,1193939}Don't worry too much.\NShe'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:57.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193939,1197484}You're telling me that,\Nbut I'm still worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.03,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207119,1209037}{\i1}Don't let it mess\Nwith your head too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.45,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209037,1211456}{\i1}I have boxing.\NYou have music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.75,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211456,1214751}{\i1}Ultimately, what matters to us\Nare the skills and the effort we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.17,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214751,1217170}{\i1}Money or social status\Nhave nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220632,1221883}Funny…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.43,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225220,1227431}Shut the hell up, ugly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:31.47,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227431,1231476}If I'm ugly face,\Nthen what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231476,1233019}Ain't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.39,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233019,1236398}I'm the number one\NNozomi-chan's supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:41.94,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236398,1241945}Oho. I'd like to say you're a great man,\Nbut take a look at yourself, Mr. White Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.19,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241945,1243196}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:47.15,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243196,1247159}If you truly wish to help Nozomi-chan, you ought\Nto be responsible for what happens to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:48.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247159,1248493}Wow, no kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.91,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248493,1250912}No. You don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.99,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250912,1252998}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:59.75,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252998,1259754}Even though I'm just some petty yakuza,\NI want to support Nozomi-chan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.42,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259754,1262424}But I don't do anything for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.30,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262424,1265302}When I run into her downtown,\NI pretend I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.30,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265302,1268305}Ha! And you call\Nyourself a supporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.39,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268305,1271391}That's why I'm telling you\Nyou're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:16.31,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271391,1276313}Don't you get that it could hurt her image\Nif she was seen with people like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.39,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276313,1278398}Huh? Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:21.98,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278398,1281985}People would tell all kind\Nof gossip she doesn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:26.86,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281985,1286865}That's why I pretend I'm strangers\Nwith Nozomi-chan everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.66,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286865,1290660}Unfortunately, this is the only way\Nwe can cheer for her: from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290660,1291328}Tatsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:34.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291328,1294498}Uh, I've never thought about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.79,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294498,1296791}What have I been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.67,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298835,1300670}Don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.21,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300670,1303215}If she doesn't come soon,\Nlet's go search for her together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303757,1306259}I'm so sorry, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306259,1309888}Please forgive your Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.07,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309888,1312073}Damn it to hell.\NLet's go look for her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.68,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313058,1314684}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.81,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315393,1317812}Don't worry, Kuma-san.\NWe no longer need to search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.85,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317812,1318855}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:08.61,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327531,1328615}Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331618,1333119}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334037,1335705}Mom, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:21.08,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335705,1341086}I am fine, but everyone was\Nvery worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341086,1342295}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.79,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343129,1344798}Nothing to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:26.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1344798,1346383}– Right?\N– Oh? Ah, y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.42,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346383,1348426}Yeah, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:31.38,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349553,1351388}Cheer up, big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:35.14,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351388,1355141}Stop hugging recycle bins.\NYou need to behave like a proper fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:38.22,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355141,1358228}Yeah. I'm Nozomi-chan's\Nnumber one supporter!
Comment: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:51.73,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1371733,1371733}Preview
